PageRank-ranked structural map of a Rust project

Usage: cs topology map [OPTIONS] [PATH]

Arguments:
  [PATH]  Path to the project root (defaults to current directory) [default: .]

Options:
      --config <PATH>              Path to configuration file
      --max-symbols <MAX_SYMBOLS>  Maximum symbols per module (0 = unlimited) [default: 0]
  -v, --verbose                    Enable verbose output
      --json                       Output in JSON format
  -h, --help                       Print help
